\v 20 Não será, pois, o <a name="03000502000008" ll="SDBH:יֹום:000006">Dia</a> do <a name="03000502000010" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> <a name="03000502000006" ll="SDBH:חֹשֶׁךְ:000000">trevas</a> e não <a name="03000502000016" ll="SDBH:אֹור:000000">luz</a>? Não será completa <a name="03000502000020" ll="SDBH:אָפֵל:000000">escuridão</a>, sem nenhuma <a name="03000502000026" ll="SDBH:נֹגַהּ:000000">claridade</a>?
    
\v 21 <a name="03000502100002" ll="SDBH:שׂנא:000000">Aborreço</a>, <a name="03000502100004" ll="SDBH:מאס:000000">desprezo</a> as <a name="03000502100006" ll="SDBH:חַג:000000">vossas</a> <a name="03000502100006" ll="SDBH:חַג:000000">festas</a> e com as <a name="03000502100016" ll="SDBH:עֲצָרָה:000000">vossas</a> <a name="03000502100016" ll="SDBH:עֲצָרָה:000000">assembleias</a> <a name="03000502100016" ll="SDBH:עֲצָרָה:000000">solenes</a> não <a name="03000502100012" ll="SDBH:רוח:000001">tenho</a> <a name="03000502100012" ll="SDBH:רוח:000001">nenhum</a> <a name="03000502100012" ll="SDBH:רוח:000001">prazer</a>. 
