\v 10 Se, porém, <a name="03000601000006" ll="SDBH:דֹּוד:001001" tl="HOTTP4228">um</a> <a name="03000601000006" ll="SDBH:דֹּוד:001001" tl="HOTTP4228">parente</a> chegado, o qual <a name="03000601000010" ll="SDBH:סרף:000000" tl="HOTTP4228">os</a> <a name="03000601000010" ll="SDBH:סרף:000000" tl="HOTTP4228">há</a> <a name="03000601000010" ll="SDBH:סרף:000000" tl="HOTTP4228">de</a> <a name="03000601000010" ll="SDBH:סרף:000000" tl="HOTTP4228">queimar</a>, <a name="03000601000014" ll="SDBH:יצא:000001">toma</a> os <a name="03000601000016" ll="SDBH:עֶצֶם:000000">cadáveres</a> para <a name="03000601000004" ll="SDBH:נשׂא:000003" tl="HOTTP4228">os</a> <a name="03000601000004" ll="SDBH:נשׂא:000003" tl="HOTTP4228">levar</a> fora da <a name="03000601000022" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000" il="HK00232;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a;NBGmk20140917">casa</a> e <a name="03000601000026" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">diz</a> ao que estiver no <a name="03000601000038" ll="SDBH:בַּיִת:000000" il="HK00232;LB00235;NBGbs20090430-1_87;NBGbs20110223-127;NBGmk20120826;NBGmk20120826a;NBGmk20140917">seu</a> <a name="03000601000034" ll="SDBH:יְרֵכָה:000000">mais</a> <a name="03000601000034" ll="SDBH:יְרֵכָה:000000">interior</a>: Haverá outro contigo? E este <a name="03000601000048" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">responder</a>: <a name="03000601000050" ll="SDBH:אֶפֶס:000000">Não</a> há; então, lhe <a name="03000601000054" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dirá</a>: <a name="03000601000056" ll="SDBH:הסה:000000">Cala</a>-<a name="03000601000056" ll="SDBH:הסה:000000">te</a>, não <a name="03000601000064" ll="SDBH:זכר:000002">menciones</a> o <a name="03000601000068" ll="SDBH:שֵׁם:000000">nome</a> do <a name="03000601000070" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a>. 
