\v 12 <a name="03000601200004" ll="SDBH:רוץ:000000">Poderão</a> <a name="03000601200004" ll="SDBH:רוץ:000000">correr</a> <a name="03000601200012" ll="SDBH:סוּס:000000" il="Fauna:2.18;LB00032">cavalos</a> na <a name="03000601200010" ll="SDBH:סֶלַע:000000">rocha</a>? E <a name="03000601200016" ll="SDBH:חרשׁ:000001" il="NBGbs20110227-95;NBGpb20140210">lavrá</a>-<a name="03000601200016" ll="SDBH:חרשׁ:000001" il="NBGbs20110227-95;NBGpb20140210">la</a> com <a name="03000601200022" ll="SDBH:בָּקָר:000000" il="Fauna:2.10;LB00022;tb032905283" tl="HOTTP4229">bois</a>? No entanto, <a name="03000601200026" ll="SDBH:הפך:000006">haveis</a> <a name="03000601200026" ll="SDBH:הפך:000006">tornado</a> o <a name="03000601200032" ll="SDBH:מִשְׁפָּט:000007">juízo</a> em <a name="03000601200030" ll="SDBH:רֹאשׁ:001001" il="Flora:5.2.5b">veneno</a> e o <a name="03000601200036" ll="SDBH:פְּרִי:000003">fruto</a> da <a name="03000601200038" ll="SDBH:צְדָקָה:000001">justiça</a>, em <a name="03000601200042" ll="SDBH:לַעֲנָה:000001" il="Flora:5.2.7b">alosna</a>. 
\v 13 Vós vos alegrais com <a name="03000601300008" ll="SDBH:לֹא דְבָר:000000" tl="HOTTP4230">Lo</a>-<a name="03000601300008" ll="SDBH:לֹא דְבָר:000000" tl="HOTTP4230">Debar</a> e <a name="03000601300012" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">dizeis</a>: Não é assim que, por <a name="03000601300020" ll="SDBH:חֹזֶק:000000">nossas</a> <a name="03000601300020" ll="SDBH:חֹזֶק:000000">próprias</a> <a name="03000601300020" ll="SDBH:חֹזֶק:000000">forças</a>, nos <a name="03000601300022">apoderamos</a> de <a name="03000601300026" ll="SDBH:קַרְנַיִם:000000">Carnaim</a>? 
