\v 6 E o <a name="03000700600004" ll="SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> <a name="03000700600002" ll="SDBH:נחם:001000">se</a> <a name="03000700600002" ll="SDBH:נחם:001000">arrependeu</a> disso. Também não acontecerá, <a name="03000700600018" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a> o <a name="03000700600020;03000700600022" ll="SDBH:אֲדֹנָי:000000;SDBH:יהוה:000000">Senhor</a> <a name="03000700600020;03000700600022" ll="SDBH:אֲדֹנָי:000000;SDBH:יהוה:000000">Deus</a>.
    
