\v 12 Então, <a name="03000701200006" ll="SDBH:אֲמַצְיָה:000003">Amazias</a> <a name="03000701200004" ll="SDBH:אמר:000000">disse</a> a <a name="03000701200010" ll="SDBH:עָמֹוס:000000">Amós</a>: <a name="03000701200014" ll="SDBH:הלך:000001">Vai</a>-<a name="03000701200014" ll="SDBH:הלך:000001">te</a>, ó <a name="03000701200012" ll="SDBH:חֹזֶה:000000">vidente</a>, <a name="03000701200016" ll="SDBH:ברח:000000">foge</a> para a <a name="03000701200022" ll="SDBH:אֶרֶץ:000000">terra</a> de <a name="03000701200024" ll="SDBH:יְהוּדָה:000000">Judá</a>, e ali <a name="03000701200028" ll="SDBH:אכל:000000">come</a> o teu <a name="03000701200032" ll="SDBH:לֶחֶם:000000" il="Tandır_bread;tb061116157">pão</a>, e ali <a name="03000701200038" ll="SDBH:נבא:000000">profetiza</a>; 
